pitch.cc: Charlie Morton showed faith in Ryan Doumit by throwing that slider in the dirt with a runner on 3rd.

Charlie Morton really has his changeup working; he's allowing a .207 average against it this season and Cubs hitters are 0-for-4 against it in this game.
